  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/0c7a11c9269fda14b2d59de07bf2f5dc.apng?t=1664320346\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/0c7a11c9269fda14b2d59de07bf2f5dc.poster.avif?t=1664320346\" class=\"bb_img\" width=374 height=448 /></picture></span><br><br>CryptoRIG is a semi-idle server management game focused on cryptocurrency mining and trading. <br>Explore a range of features including:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Managing servers from a resource and operation context.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/d40ae91d467d20b406d154b50c7d643f.poster.avif?t=1664320346\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/d40ae91d467d20b406d154b50c7d643f.webm?t=1664320346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/d40ae91d467d20b406d154b50c7d643f.mp4?t=1664320346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>High level management of server clusters.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/47fe9a3efc6e871f9c0c926da7799e39.poster.avif?t=1664320346\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/47fe9a3efc6e871f9c0c926da7799e39.webm?t=1664320346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/47fe9a3efc6e871f9c0c926da7799e39.mp4?t=1664320346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Extensive research and progression opportunities to work your way up to mining more lucrative cryptocurrencies. </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/1c74788e3db061ef3027225dfc5b3555.poster.avif?t=1664320346\" width=650 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/1c74788e3db061ef3027225dfc5b3555.webm?t=1664320346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/1c74788e3db061ef3027225dfc5b3555.mp4?t=1664320346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br></li><li><strong>Procedurally generated cryptocurrencies with simulated market trends.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Fast paced intra-day trading of simulated cryptocurrencies.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/3878cd3adb6a010a866d0053edb4bb0f.poster.avif?t=1664320346\" width=550 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/3878cd3adb6a010a866d0053edb4bb0f.webm?t=1664320346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/3878cd3adb6a010a866d0053edb4bb0f.mp4?t=1664320346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Automated trading based on user defined rules.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/9bd0f21f099455786dfab71473bd3a79.poster.avif?t=1664320346\" width=550 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/9bd0f21f099455786dfab71473bd3a79.webm?t=1664320346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/9bd0f21f099455786dfab71473bd3a79.mp4?t=1664320346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Procedurally generated random events.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/2fbce597e6da5b592abcb46197af3b0b.poster.avif?t=1664320346\" width=500 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/2fbce597e6da5b592abcb46197af3b0b.webm?t=1664320346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/2fbce597e6da5b592abcb46197af3b0b.mp4?t=1664320346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Steam achievements</strong><br></li><li><strong>Multiple game scenarios with varying difficulties and play styles</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/4bd2c4595ce10b757bef03f9a4843b31.avif?t=1664320346\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>Challenge yourself on the QUADSTAT VX exchange, manage endless instances of servers, shield yourself from the random, chaotic world events and optimise your cryptoRIG to take over the market!</strong><br><br><strong> We look forward to getting your feedback and driving the final stages of game development. As always happy trading and HODL!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/066d9e36d71baa3ee14dc2d21ae872b5.poster.avif?t=1664320346\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801950/extras/066d9e36d71baa3ee14dc2d21ae872b5.webm?t=1664320346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></li></ul>",
